  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/43a8878f7be95700e9dae4d2876a55b2.avif?t=1773734932\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buckle up, pilot! We're stationed above an alien planet surrounded with an abandoned <strong>mining system</strong> and filled with alien bugs. Your mission? Dive into the tamed sectors, use the mining system <strong>to collect upgrade parts</strong> and <strong>extract the Bioshards</strong> from alien minerals. Beware— the system is infested with alien bug cells <strong>spreading and waiting to hatch.</strong> Stay quick on your feet, and you might just make it out in one piece!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.poster.avif?t=1773734932\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.webm?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.mp4?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEWARE OF THE SWARM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of every expedition, <strong>the map is procedurally generated</strong>, and it's crawling with alien bugs. The cells constantly <strong>spread and evolve.</strong> When triggered, <strong>the bugs burst out from the cells</strong> to swarm you down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.poster.avif?t=1773734932\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.webm?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.mp4?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE TO BUILD SYNERGIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip up to five skills each run: active ones that strike automatically or passive ones that boost your abilities. Upgrade each skill differently to <strong>maximize their potential.</strong> Discover <strong>unique synergies</strong> between skills and upgrades to optimize your build. The better your synergies, the easier you'll crush enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/f61327b0bcb9ae07296dd4f84bf4397b.poster.avif?t=1773734932\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/f61327b0bcb9ae07296dd4f84bf4397b.webm?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/f61327b0bcb9ae07296dd4f84bf4397b.mp4?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique horde trigger mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 characters with rank missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 maps with 7 evolution difficulties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 skills with 120+ unique upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Gadgets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 items with rarities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 enemy varieties with 2 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/afb30b8020eefade6102a0f616c3a4db.avif?t=1773734932\" width=614 height=180 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buckle up, pilot! We're stationed above an alien planet surrounded with an abandoned <strong>mining system</strong> and filled with alien bugs. Your mission? Dive into the tamed sectors, use the mining system <strong>to collect upgrade parts</strong> and <strong>extract the Bioshards</strong> from alien minerals. Beware— the system is infested with alien bug cells <strong>spreading and waiting to hatch.</strong> Stay quick on your feet, and you might just make it out in one piece!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.poster.avif?t=1773734932\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.webm?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/fab26e8abcf69d15376c3112694a2c46.mp4?t=1773734932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEWARE OF THE SWARM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of every expedition, <strong>the map is procedurally generated</strong>, and it's crawling with alien bugs. The cells constantly <strong>spread and evolve.</strong> When triggered, <strong>the bugs burst out from the cells</strong> to swarm you down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5543989cf6d905d4f761ad77fa3d7000.poster.avif?t=1773734932\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/5