" >Operator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25+ achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375900/extras/afb30b8020eefade6102a0f616c3a4db.avif?t=1773734932\" width=614 height=180 /></span></p>",
